            <lg xml:id="TK353">
<l>aiyatti ṉīṅkit teḷintārkku vaiyattiṉ</l>
<l>vāṉa naṇiya tuṭaittu</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Heaven is nearer than earth to those men of purified minds who are freed from from doubt.</l>
